data.title: Energia All-Ireland League Men’s Divisions: Round 11 Results Round-Up
data.text:
Table toppers Clontarf and St. Mary’s College both tasted defeat for the first time in this season’s Energia All-Ireland League, Dublin University opened their win account, and unbeaten Instonians burst through the 500-point mark with a 14-try haul against Dolphin.
